des: The Clarity Program from Doc Williams and Build With Me helps you turn your idea into an online business. This voice experience takes you on this journey to your new business through 10 days of guidance and motivation. You can open the Clarity Program directly or by asking Alexa for a specific day. For example, "Alexa, ask Doc Williams for Day 4"
